reviewText: They won't play on the new DVD player, because code number on tape, very displeased I can't use these tape, sad!!!!

My bad. I was in a hurry and not paying close enough attention when I ordered to realize these DVDs will not play on my DVD player which was purchased in the US. I live in Region 1 of the world and these play only in Region 2.  Big bummer. I love these movies.
